(fetchWidth, area_cell_area).explanation: Wider fetch units require more transistors and larger instruction buffers, directly increasing the physical cell area of the processor;

(fetchWidth, power_register).explanation: Wider fetch requires more register file ports and larger instruction buffers, increasing register-related power consumption;

(fetchWidth, nL2TLBEntries).explanation: Fetch width and L2 TLB entries are independent design parameters that don't directly influence each other;
